          "title": "An official limited-time island based on **Disneyland** is coming to Fortnite today - The island, which is titled Disneyland Game Rush, launches at 8am PT / 11am ET / 4pm GMT. Players will be able to find it by either searching for its name or using its specific island code, which is 4617-4819-8826. The island will open with a central hub, from which players can visit seven mini-games, each based on a different Disneyland ride",
